race.comment: CUP OF AMBITION (7) is a 28-start maiden having first run for the new barn. Formerly with the Parry yard and has the form to feature here if presented wound up. Stablemate CORVALIST (2) was disappointing at Dalby last time so given a let-up. Another new addition to the Parry yard has a host of minors to his name and can run well in his first start at this circuit. KOUKLITSA (9) is an experienced dirt track performer resuming. Has good speed and will give a sight. UNDER SUSPICION (14) is a five-start maiden having his first start in this area for the new yard and is drawn for a good run. LORD VALEN (3) Is a nine-time placegetter in 15 career starts but still looking for a maiden success. Could get his chance here.
